  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.5.8">
<l>peṇṇāki yiṉṉamutam vañcit tāṉaip piṟaiyeyiṟṟaṉ ṟaṭalariyāyp peruki ṉāṉai</l>
<l>taṇṇārnta vārppuṉalcūḻ meyya meṉṉun taṭavaraimēl kiṭantāṉaip paṇaṅkaḷ mēvi</l>
<l>yeṇṇāṉai yeṇṇiṟanta pukaḻi ṉāṉai yilaṅkoḷicē raravintam pōṉṟu nīṇṭa</l>
<l>kaṇṇāṉaik kaṇṇārak kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ kaṭipoḻilcūḻ kaṭalmallait talaca yaṉattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, as a girl, snatched the sweet ambrosia, [and] who appeared once</l>
<l rend="indent">as a powerful lion with curved fangs,</l>
<l>The one who sleeps on the broad mountain called Meyyam,</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by cool, full flowing waters,</l>
<l rend="indent">him who is inconceivable abiding on a cobra’s hood,</l>
<l>The one whose praises are beyond counting, and whose elongated eyes</l>
<l rend="indent">are like bright, shining lotuses,</l>
<l>I saw for myself, as I filled [my] eyes, in Talacayaṉam</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by fragrant gardens at Mallai by the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
